<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt2" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"redirect","href":"./Template:Redirect"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Current Events"},"2":{"wt":"the album by John Abercrombie"},"3":{"wt":"Current Events (album){{!}}&apos;&apos;Current Events&apos;&apos; (album)"},"4":{"wt":"the portal"},"5":{"wt":"Portal:Current Events"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAw">"Current Events" redirects here. For the album by John Abercrombie, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Current_Events_(album)" title="Current Events (album)"><i>Current Events</i> (album)</a>. For the portal, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Portal:Current_Events" title="Portal:Current Events" class="mw-redirect">Portal:Current Events</a>.</div>
<link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Wikipedia_indefinitely_move-protected_pages#News" about="#mwt3" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"pp-move-indef","href":"./Template:Pp-move-indef"},"params":{"small":{"wt":"yes"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBA"/>
