<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Interpretive_journalism" title="Interpretive journalism">Interpretive</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Investigative_journalism" title="Investigative journalism">Investigative</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Muckraker" title="Muckraker">Muckraking</a></li>
