<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./New_Journalism" title="New Journalism">New Journalism</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Non-profit_journalism" title="Non-profit journalism">Non-profit</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Online_journalism" title="Online journalism" class="mw-redirect">Online</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Opinion_journalism" title="Opinion journalism">Opinion</a></li>
